# LangChain Ecosystem Workshop

> Learning project for the Cursor Agent Factory AI Learning Path
> **Workshops**: L7 LangChain + L3 LangGraph + L16 LangSmith

## Project Context

This is a **learning workshop** covering the LangChain ecosystem:
- **LangChain** (0.3+): Agent framework, LCEL chains, tools
- **LangGraph** (0.2+): Stateful workflows, multi-agent orchestration
- **LangSmith**: Observability, evaluation, prompt iteration

